    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a superior standard of automotive care. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation meet our rigorous dealership criteria. Boasting a well-documented service history and a refined interior, this vehicle offers an exceptional balance of luxury and long-term reliability. We invite discerning clients to experience the sophisticated performance and enduring value of this high-caliber selection.",
      "price": 38500.0,
