    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels fantastic? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s been really well-loved and well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner immediately! Whether you're commuting or planning a road trip, this car is ready for it all. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 34500.0,
