    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2017 Ford Focus RS, a pinnacle of the modern hot hatch era. This unit features the high-output 2.3L EcoBoost I4 engine equipped with a low-inertia twin-scroll turbocharger, delivering power through a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The standout performance feature is the Ford Performance All-Wheel Drive system with Dynamic Torque Vectoring, which utilizes twin electronically controlled clutch packs to manage torque distribution across the rear axle for exceptional turn-in. The chassis is equipped with dual-mode adjustable dampers and four-piston Brembo front calipers clamping down on 350mm ventilated rotors. This vehicle has been maintained to ensure consistent boost pressure and drivetrain integrity, making it a formidable driver\u2019s car for those who value technical sophistication and raw performance.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Maintenance records available. Clean interior. Mechanically sound. Firm price.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances luxury and reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though I want to note a few minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well that is only visible upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light, natural softening on the driver\u2019s seat. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the heated seats and navigation, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car has been treated with the highest care. It comes with a complete service history, documenting regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires are in excellent condition with significant tread remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been cared for by a non-smoker and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
