      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a sophisticated synthesis of performance and reliability. Having undergone rigorous mechanical scrutiny, it presents in commendable condition, offering the discerning driver a refined experience and proven durability. Secure an exceptional investment in automotive excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
