    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable car for me and is still in really solid shape. It drives beautifully and has been well-loved, so you know you\u2019re getting something dependable. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I'm honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
