    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the 3.6L flat-six boxer engine mated to a 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers exceptional throttle response, recently verified with a clean DME overrev report. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS) to ensure drivetrain longevity. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup with PASM active damping. Braking performance is sharp via four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the structural integrity is flawless, and the staggered alloys are shod in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car optimized for lateral grip and high-RPM engagement.",
      "price": 31850.0,
